WEBVTT

00:00.320 --> 00:00.800
Enough

00:01.640 --> 00:02.960
This matter ends here

00:03.440 --> 00:04.960
Those involved in the seditious poem

00:04.960 --> 00:06.160
Have all been executed

00:06.280 --> 00:07.320
None left

00:08.920 --> 00:09.920
As for Yu Gong

00:14.840 --> 00:17.760
The Imperial City Guard watches you closely

00:18.680 --> 00:20.200
As soon as Chu Huan mobilized men

00:20.200 --> 00:21.960
They immediately submitted a report

00:22.520 --> 00:23.040
To

00:23.160 --> 00:24.080
My desk

00:31.280 --> 00:31.920
You

00:32.680 --> 00:34.040
Act decisively

00:34.040 --> 00:35.160
Strike ruthlessly

00:35.320 --> 00:36.320
Eloquent

00:36.800 --> 00:37.680
Ungrateful

00:37.920 --> 00:38.520
Father

00:40.080 --> 00:41.160
In this world

00:41.840 --> 00:43.440
You're not the only clever one

00:44.000 --> 00:45.360
I say, second son

00:45.840 --> 00:47.720
One mistake is acceptable

00:48.040 --> 00:49.280
But not a second time

00:50.600 --> 00:51.440
That Yu Gong

00:51.840 --> 00:52.920
Let it rest for now

00:56.320 --> 00:58.000
You haven't been to the palace in a while

00:58.640 --> 00:59.320
Accompany me

00:59.600 --> 01:00.600
For a game of chess

01:01.720 --> 01:02.760
Yes, Father
